{"tid":1116732,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性分析) 香港嘅醫療定台灣嘅醫療好啲？","createTime":"2019-04-20T07:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T14:27:45.000Z","uid":189465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9c3aa158b14af00b94054c0b9424c1fe717300","tid":1116732,"uid":189465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"某位自稱喺台灣住咗10年嘅香港人Youtube拍片<br />\n話台灣嘅醫療制度比香港好 睇醫生平啲<br />\n然後下面就一大班台狗打哂飛機<br />\n所以就想問下<br />\n綜合醫療福利 技術 制度等等<br />\n大家覺得香港好啲定台灣好啲？"},{"pid":"3bee7bbd197b1c24723529f8ee51317de976997a","tid":1116732,"uid":54270,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6a9c3aa158b14af00b94054c0b9424c1fe717300","tid":1116732,"uid":189465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"某位自稱喺台灣住咗10年嘅香港人Youtube拍片<br />\n話台灣嘅醫療制度比香港好 睇醫生平啲<br />\n然後下面就一大班台狗打哂飛機<br />\n所以就想問下<br />\n綜合醫療福利 技術 制度等等<br />\n大家覺得香港好啲定台灣好啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"台灣"},{"pid":"041825d8b4fc61e7d7db686b083b6fafbbc5c764","tid":1116732,"uid":54270,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"淨係時間公立都好過香港<br />\n我之前喉嚨有野卡住個感覺<br />\n<br />\n想睇香港睇時預約,但返台灣開學之前都未有消息<br />\n<br />\n返咗台灣後,即日有得睇,仲好快book埋期做小手術<br />\n<br />\n係11月個時我老母打俾我收信先同我講要排18個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91842c8b6d27cb712cf2cc57f046c22c28b61fc6","tid":1116732,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"公立：台灣&gt;香港<br />\n私家：香港&gt;台灣"},{"pid":"2676d62c9ca90d549a2dc92e72eada68e210105a","tid":1116732,"uid":246417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"明顯台灣"},{"pid":"b78e38d5947d64c2705d005b3bd987e902cad35f","tid":1116732,"uid":42852,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"依家屋企人身體出事，都會去台灣睇，質素好之餘，計埋機票都平過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a3b5e0d29fe18daf6a215f91dea75d7fc30bc2","tid":1116732,"uid":196266,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"全球前200大醫院裡面，台灣佔咗14間，全球排第三，亞洲第一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2005: Nobel Prize winner Paul Krugman: &quot;Taiwan's Health Insurance system is the best system on earth.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nPaul Krugman, the 2008 Nobel Prize-winning economist, often takes Taiwan's National Health Insurance as an example of excellent healthcare system. He suggests that the United State should carry out similar healthcare systems.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣醫保係全世界數一數二，香港真係望塵莫及<br />\n<br />\n攞台灣醫療同香港比，就好似巴塞對傑志，冇得鬥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主觀嘅經驗，我係台灣住咗三年，我洗牙只係要一百幾台幣。感冒睇醫生都係好平，而且啲醫生唔趕時間，會問得好詳細，仲會同你吹下水。<br />\n啲藥唔會好似香港咁一袋袋，而係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzXCAzw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzXCAzw.png&h=855afb61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包你唔會食漏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓上有人話香港私家好過台灣，因為我住九龍塘附近，我屋企離浸會好近，所以我平時都係睇私家。我真心唔覺得香港私家好過台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7091432ae7f60a855ad38e1148e98487369af21f","tid":1116732,"uid":71583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"廿年前，都仲覺得香港醫療好<br />\n依家竟然係同台灣比較，仲要被比下去<br />\n好快香港嘅目標唔係台灣，10年後有人會開post問香港醫療定大灣區醫療好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1314c76a6d3f1c3f92a2bc2489a8f363fb9c6f22","tid":1116732,"uid":240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"剩係台妹護士都贏左<br />\n香港邊有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a73f916b3fa1a18991cb084abfcb18feaee936e","tid":1116732,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"436cf8db3d4e2739d18786578f74c06f854084a0","tid":1116732,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"病人角度: 台灣&gt;香港<br />\n醫護角度: 一樣垃圾"},{"pid":"5d6c8ca06cfcd1ec15f6b1be71a8cec3f1c9d2ac","tid":1116732,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:59:29.000Z","msg":"估唔到台灣仲好過香港, 唉!"},{"pid":"7470d6e8d214b9d02ddb2232eaeecef427bb9542","tid":1116732,"uid":3112,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"436cf8db3d4e2739d18786578f74c06f854084a0","tid":1116732,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"病人角度: 台灣&gt;香港<br />\n醫護角度: 一樣垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"香港醫護自視過高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e413bb83994bea16a7ae0df201f3d4692b717d","tid":1116732,"uid":242872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}